snippet.title: Kao the Kangaroo - Release the Power of the Gloves!
snippet.description:
A secret once thought buried, a mighty pair of boxing gloves imbued with power over the elements seems like a blessing... or are they? Harness the power of the gloves to defeat Kao’s enemies, traverse through the world, and help uncover the truth behind Kao’s father’s disappearance! 

Kao The Kangaroo releases May 27th, 2022, on Playstation, Xbox, Nintendo Switch and PC. For more info visit https://kaokangaroo.com/

Stay tuned to our social media for updates!

Twitter - https://twitter.com/Kaothekangaroo
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/KaoTheKangaroo
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/kaothekangaroo
Discord - https://discord.gg/D79aQUJXdM
Kao on Steam: https://bit.ly/3JeXcJh

Kao the Kangaroo - What a Wonderful World: https://youtu.be/DEG4UGtRT0M
Kao the Kangaroo - Announcement Trailer: https://youtu.be/lwFocmxxbAY
The Evolution of Kao the Kangaroo: https://youtu.be/v3Ka1HyjDQc
